            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="43667745">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">年轻人塑造什么样特质？
“卓尔不群”</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-05-06 13:04</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                年轻人塑造什么样特质？<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>“卓尔不群”
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
